```

3. Verify that the function names match the endpoint names used in the frontend `url_for()` calls exactly.

4. Confirm that all templates referenced exist and are named correctly.

By ensuring these routes exist and correspond exactly to the frontend URLs, the website will be directly operable at http://localhost:5000 with the dashboard as the first page, and navigation will work correctly.

